 <p>Saltaire is a cu de sac subdivision that runs from Rte 12 to the ocean with 59 lots on either side of Marlin Dr. Saltaire does not have an active home owners association but a small fee is collected to help maintain the private road and the beach access. Saltaire is located in Duck just past <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/poteskeet-village.asp" title="Poteskeet Village">Poteskeet Village</a> and before you get to <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/bayberry-bluffs.asp" title="Bayberry Bluff">Bayberry Bluff</a>. </p>
